    J

    JAddin - Class in Unnamed Package
    This JAddin class - together with the JAddinThread class - is a framework used to create HCL Domino server add-in programs.
    JAddin() - Constructor for class JAddin
    This constructor is called by the HCL Domino RunJava task if no arguments are specified.
    JAddin(String[]) - Constructor for class JAddin
    This constructor is called by the HCL Domino RunJava task if any command line arguments is specified.
    JAddinThread - Class in Unnamed Package
    This abstract class must be implemented by the user add-in.
    JAddinThread() - Constructor for class JAddinThread
